and consistently,


9
00:00:30,597 --> 00:00:32,633 line:-1
becoming second nature to us.


10
00:00:32,666 --> 00:00:35,435 line:-2
Without relying on them,
we will find it very difficult


11
00:00:35,469 --> 00:00:37,171 line:-1
